        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued October 18 at 2:44PM CDT by NWS Chicago IL</headline>
        <description>At 242 PM CDT, trained weather spotters reported a funnel cloud in a
cluster of showers over Ladd, or 7 miles northwest of Peru, moving
east at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Funnel clouds.

SOURCE...Trained weather spotters.

IMPACT...Isolated damage to roofs, siding and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Prairie Center, Leland, Earlville, Triumph, Harding, Troy Grove,
Peru, Lake Holiday, Somonauk, Mendota, and La Salle.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
